# Contributing

Thank you for considering contributing.

This repository prioritizes quality and clarity over quantity.

## What to add

Resources should be:
- genuinely useful in real family life
- clearly described in one sentence
- not overly commercial or trend-driven

## Format

Use the standard format:

- [Name](link) – Short, clear description.

## Guidelines

- Keep descriptions concise
- Avoid duplication
- Place items in the correct category
- Maintain alphabetical order within sections

## Philosophy

This is not a comprehensive directory.  
It is a curated system.

If in doubt, prioritize:
clarity, usefulness, and longevity.
